How can I set up track subscription permissions where:
1. One specific participant (agent) should only be able to subscribe to a specific audio track
2. All other participants should be able to subscribe to all tracks EXCEPT that specific audio track
```js
if (localParticipant && localAudioTrack) {
    try {
        // Set default permission to false (deny all by default)
        localParticipant.setTrackSubscriptionPermissions(false, [
            // For agent: can only subscribe to localAudioTrack
            {
                participantIdentity: getAgentParticipantId(),
                allowedTrackSids: [localAudioTrack.sid]
            },
            // For all other participants: allow all tracks except localAudioTrack
            {
                participantIdentity: '*',
                allowAll: true  // allow all tracks for non-agent participants
            }
        ]);
    } catch (error) {
        console.error('Error setting track subscription permissions:', error);
    }
}
```
